        "niveau": "easy",
        "reponse": "L\u0027\u00E9tendue $E = D_{max} - D_{min} = 12,6 - 12,3 = 0,3\\ \\text{mm}$. L\u0027incertitude absolue $\\Delta D = \\frac{E}{2} = 0,15\\ \\text{mm}$.",
        "sousQuestions": []
