        "texte": "Calculer l\u0027incertitude relative $\\frac{\\Delta D}{\\bar{D}}$ en pourcentage. Donner le r\u00E9sultat arrondi \u00E0 $1\\%$ pr\u00E8s.",
        "niveau": "medium",
